This paper is about a conversational assistant that combines crowd-powered and automated approaches. The paper discusses the architecture and deployment of the system, which involves natural language processing, machine learning, and human-computer interaction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Additionally, the paper involves aspects of cybersecurity (cs.CY) and social and information networks (cs.SI), which are also possible categories.
